window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>“We were a thousand miles away from home when the car gave up the ghost....”</p> <p>When Jack’s car breaks down in the middle of a cross-country road trip, the mysterious house at the top of the hill is a beacon of hope. If he can borrow a phone to call for help, he’ll be on his way in no time. But someone - or something - has other plans. Soon, Jack finds himself trapped in a nightmare that defies logic, where a depraved killer on the loose is the least of his problems. Will Jack escape before it’s too late?</p> <p>A house full of strangers.</p> <p>An unsolvable mystery.</p> <p>A night that won’t end.</p> <p>Welcome to Bedside Manor.</p>"; 
